data.description: Charming Victorian home in historic Park View! Prime corner lot with an expansive backyard. Inside you are welcomed with 10ft ceilings and gleaming hardwood floors, plus beautifully upgraded kitchen. This home is truly the perfect blend of classic charm and modern convenience. Layout features a formal living room, dining room and den on the first level, plus kitchen and full bath. Second level offers 3 generously sized bedrooms and a full upgraded hall bathroom. Great location conveniently located near Naval Hospital and minutes from interstate.
